column5: I still check in and lurk here and there   Fishing strictly salt water now on Long lsland but man l do miss them pike this time of year.  FHR
Happy belated, Wayne!  Hope you had a fantastic weekend, adn a great year ahead
Happy birthday Wayne. Hope you have a great weekend. You only turn 50 once...unless your 100  .
happy birthday Wayne!!! God bless you !!!
Have a great birthday Wayne.
May the best of your past be the worst of your future. Happy Birthday.
Welcome to the Old Pharts club. Better start buying stock in Geritol and Depends

Thanks for all the Birthday Wishes.. great to bring some silent folks out of the wood work and to know fellas like FHR are still amongst us. Like my shirt, bought tonight at Rama, says.. "I'm not dead yet"!  50's not a big deal.. this beat up old body feels like it's 85 anyhow!!
Happy birthday old man.
Hope you had a great day, Wayne. Many more to you.
Happy belated B-Day Wayne, hope it was a goodun !!
Happy birthday Wayne.  We share the same date.  I'm 59 (on Friday), posting this on Saturday.  Thanx for the link to Temagami Marine, I've been in contact with Des.
50? i swear you dont look a day over 80....good on ya...
Well at least I now know what I was celebrating last night.....  Happy belated old (yet younger than me) man.
I think we should start a collection for a fancy cane  Happy B-Day Wayne!
Good idea. Cork handle. Mi6 graphite. It would be nice and light. Spiel has already made some mock ups for this ageing group of anglers.
I might be able to help with that.
Bet you had good birthday Wayne. Brought FHR out of woodwork for the occasion.
hbd wayne
All the best to you Wayne... I hope you had a good one...
happy birthday wayne
Happy belated Birthday old Man!  I wish you all the best,  G
Thanks guys!  G.. I'm sure you and old Spiel even tipped a beer in my honour! LOL !
Just one?
Talking bottle or case...
Crate.  Happy Birthday brother... I hope you have many more  G.
Well I got two more than my sister.. I hope I get many more yet!
A little birdie told me your ... umm... well... 50 today.... One good thing.. you'll always be older than ME!!!  Hope you have a great day! Its Friday! NO RELIVING YOUR YOUTH!!
my God that's old  oh wait..no it's not have a great birthday
Have a great birthday,I am one up on you this past week! They say life begins at 50!!!!!,What were we doing before?
Happy Birthday old man....
HA,HA.Your old. Congrates.
Happy birthday Wayne have a good time and get out and enjoy the day.   Art
Happy day me OLD Irish brudder!
I remember 50, Have a good one!
Happy Birthday you old snagger!
Enjoy a craft beer or top quality scotch or wine or a margerita or box wine or an OE
Happy birthday Wayne, bet hes going to the honeymoon capital again
Hope you had a great day.
Have a good one Wayne.  Who's giving you the B-Day spankings this year?
Happy Birthday!!
Happy Birthday Wayne. Hope your having a great day with the family and some drinks.
Oh to be 50 again.  Do something special - then tell all.    Have a great one
Happy Birthday Hun!!   Hope you have a great one
Happy Birthday Wayne, I hope it was a great day  Maureen
Well, I hope you got everything you wanted for your birthday!  Wishing you all the very best!
Happy Birthday Old Man!   FHR
all the best wayne......congrads on the BIG  50!!!
50!!!!! Cripes, i still have body parts older than that !!!!Not many though
since when is 50 old?  Happy birthday Wayne!
Ya got 13 years on me Wayne, but Happy B-Day from us here in Brantford!
Happy b day Wayne hope your having a good one
